1. Dok* je ona govorila, ja sam se osmehnuo. (While she was talking, I smiled.)
2. On je često razmišljao dok* sedeo u parku. (He often thought while sitting in the park.)
3. Da li ćeš doći dok* budeš imala vremena? (Will you come while you have time?)
4. Čitam knjigu dok* čekam da jelo završi. (I am reading a book while waiting for the meal to finish.)
5. Dok* smo čekali, razgovarali smo o najnovijim vestima. (While we were waiting, we talked about the latest news.)